column16: Brett Gardner homers (18) on a line drive to right field.
Todd Frazier flies out to left fielder Corey Dickerson.
Ronald Torreyes out on a sacrifice bunt, first baseman Logan Morrison to second baseman Tim Beckham.   Chase Headley to 2nd.
Mike Napoli pops out to third baseman Evan Longoria.
Adrian Beltre singles on a ground ball to right fielder Steven Souza Jr.   Nomar Mazara to 2nd.

Rajai Davis reaches on a fielder's choice out, shortstop Tim Beckham to catcher Wilson Ramos to third baseman Evan Longoria to pitcher Andrew Kittredge.   Matt Chapman out at 3rd.    Jaycob Brugman to 3rd.    Rajai Davis to 2nd.
Jaycob Brugman singles on a bunt ground ball to pitcher Andrew Kittredge.   Jed Lowrie scores.    Matt Chapman to 3rd on the throw.
Matt Chapman singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Mallex Smith.   Jed Lowrie to 3rd.
Bruce Maxwell pops out to third baseman Evan Longoria in foul territory.
Jed Lowrie doubles (28) on a line drive to right fielder Shane Peterson.
Marcus Semien grounds into a force out, second baseman Brad Miller to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.   Rajai Davis out at 2nd.    Marcus Semien to 1st.
Rajai Davis singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Peter Bourjos.
